<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>04/2025</strong></span></p>
</td>
<td valign="top" width="159">
<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1,40%</strong></span></p>
